Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:04.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:12.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the last miraculous \Npresent of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief! \NWhere are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:49.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't have time \Nto toy with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's been gone for three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.52,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,The Phantom Thief Has Vanished\NThree months since \NKid the Phantom Thief's last crime\NRetired?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is he? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's just been three months. \NMaybe he hasn't gone anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:37.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:43.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Has he ever taken this much time off \Nbetween robberies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There must be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.67,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,Three months since \NKid the Phantom Thief's last crime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:55.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector, isn't it a good thing that \NKid the Phantom Thief isn't busy stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:57.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch Kid with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:06.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like you want \NKid the Phantom Thief to commit crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should tell the commissioner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:11.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, I don't think you need to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:17.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, say what you will. \NWe owe Inspector Nakamori a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:23.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When we switched shifts on that \Nlast stakeout, he brought me ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He brought me a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I want you to give serious thought \Nas to why Kid hasn't shown up lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He probably has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:41.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you guys morons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:14.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Holy Night: Two Kid the Phantom Thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:19.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. First I get a cold, then finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought idiots were too slow\N to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:45.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez! You're in a bad mood, Dad's in a snit \Nbecause Kid's been a no-show lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have to worry about both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's mad about Kid's {\i1}absence{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:53.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd think the cops would have no \Nproblem with a thief {\i1}not{\i0} stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:57.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad thinks it's weird that Kid hasn't \Nbeen around for three months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sounds like your old man's the weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:05.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure even Kid the Phantom Thief doesn't \Nfeel like stealing from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:09.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Man, I've got my own problems to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii-chan, who always gathers \Nintel on the Big Jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,was bedridden after straining his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, blow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:29.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, I wonder where that \Nsneak thief is hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:35.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, right when Jii-chan got better, \NI get hit with a cold and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:41.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Given all that, was I supposed to keep up \Nmy end and pull off regular robberies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That third-rate inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:47.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What does he think I am, a weekly \Nmanga magazine or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be it! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Talk about no tact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've finally got my health back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:21.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right. Time to look into \Nwhat the Young Master requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:28.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. That is indeed a valuable jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:33.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but at best, it's a gem \Nworth tens of millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,not a Big Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:42.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master seems to be busy at school, \Nso I can save this report for another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone! It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:48.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief Has Issued a Notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief has released a notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:54.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At 6:54 pm this evening, Christmas Eve,\N Kid the Phantom Thief stole
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the Star of the Giants that was decorating \NTofu Department Store's Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is! He finally struck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:03.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}The star is inlaid with emeralds \Nworth several billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's meant to be donated to \Na museum after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I'm talkin' about, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:12.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Don't talk like that in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:18.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All cars, mobilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get to the Tofu Department Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Something must've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, we have to get to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:47.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Customers are coming in droves,\N just like I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:53.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With this many people, \Nsales should double... no, quadruple!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Releasing a fake letter \Nwas a stroke of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If Kid doesn't actually show up, \Nwe'll lose face and sales afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:08.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief wouldn't \Nlet his prey escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:17.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're gonna play Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Relax. I'll prepare your escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:27.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But I don't know if I can \Ndo something so outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you steal that Star of the Giants,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:35.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,we can hold onto it {\i1}and{\i0} reap the huge \Nreward of the amount it's insured for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:39.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the whole thing will be pinned on Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Succeed, and I'll make you my vice-president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,V-Vice-president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Special Bonus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Special Bonus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Isn't that enough, Aoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hang in there! You're so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-This spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:23.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-A little to the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Then here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez! That's left, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You suck at this, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, everyone \Nwill be here before it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For cryin' out loud, it's not \Nlike you're a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:43.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do you gotta hold a \NChristmas party every year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can do what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You and your parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:55.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's excitement in the air \Nat Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:57.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are two more hours \Nuntil the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, quit being lazy and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will he really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief Sent Advance Notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fork and spoon go opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How the hell should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:12.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's interview Inspector Nakamori, \Nwho's in charge of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector, Kid has made a move at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:21.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! I'll pulverize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was Inspector Nakamori, in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:34.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can see all the people gathered \Ndown below from our chopper camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:37.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you viewers at home \Nknow what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:41.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This crowd of onlookers has Kid fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's no understatement to say that Kid is \Nthe greatest phantom thief of this generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the invite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You came too, Akako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:59.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just thought it would be immature \Nnot to come after you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:03.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you all came. Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:07.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear? Kid is appearing tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:12.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Kid for you, showing up \Non Christmas Eve! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:16.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh. All that brouhaha was over\N Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll get to see your dad all hot and \Nbothered with frustration again, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:50.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Kid calls have begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:57.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:03.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kid! I'm gonna be \Nthe one who captures you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:09.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't skip town on me \Nwithout previous notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:25.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, I've got a lot of food over here,\N so everyone eat your fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:30.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She just put out store-bought stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No need to tell them that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We've got cake, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Flutter-flutter-flutter! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now who would be calling at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Does anybody have a lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, nobody here would have a lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll just have to \Nborrow one from Aoko's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I thought I'd have Dad sing us a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:22.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said he's gonna be late tonight \Nbecause of Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, good for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, so how could Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're at Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:39.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid T-shirts, sweatshirts, and other \Nmerchandise are selling like hotcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:45.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Zaizen, the owner \Nof Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:51.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts on the advance \Nnotice you received from Kid today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't recall sending out \Nany advance notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me! \NAnd... why {\i1}are{\i0} you asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito and Akako-chan! \NWhat are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:10.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But what about this \Nunexpectedly huge sales boost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:16.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If they just got notice today, \Nwhy do they have all those Kid goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like Kid is everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:27.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It just goes to show that even a sneak \Nthief like that can do some good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:31.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid is bad, but this owner is no better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, he couldn't just stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to those cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But Kid isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:02.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:09.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:17.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's already past the appointed time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:36.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Kid! Kid the Phantom Thief is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is too much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Vice-president! \NYou can be vice-president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:20.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, that includes a major raise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus a chauffeur and flexible working hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:36.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But that's not all! The vice-prez gets \Nto take home food from the gourmet floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take the Star of the Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:46.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:50.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:53.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew he could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just had to hold his hand most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give up, Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?! I've never seen \Nyou before in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't know when to give up, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief, you're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! Kid isn't all he's cracked up to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:43.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please continue to shop at \NTofu Department Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:55.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:06.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Good luck, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Which is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:28.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I came, just as the advance \Nnotice stated, Mr. Zaizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A night when miracles can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me a miracle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:42.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll climb the tree, so wait \Nfor me up there, Kid-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:46.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-With a suave line like that, \Nthis must be the real Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:53.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. But first, how about I \Ngive you a Christmas present?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:32.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-M-My department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to vanish again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:52.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...you suddenly disappeared \Nwithout any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:56.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And eight years passed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:08.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run or hide,\N Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Let's meet again," he says! The idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, I'll tan your hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You look happy, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:45.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Start to wind it up, you guys,\N before it gets late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kaito?! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I had to run an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And on the way back, I bought an ornament \Nfor your tree, so cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So how about some grub?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:04.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm runnin' on empty here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We finished everything already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:37.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The program you witnessed this evening \Nwas the miracle of a holy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Truth that sprang from a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:43.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you enjoyed it, then I'm \Nsatisfied as a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:47.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:24.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hi, Aoko Nakamori here! \NI'm doing the preview today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:26.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the next episode, we all go skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:30.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan puts the moves on Kaito \Non the pure white ski slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:33.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That Kaito is pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder what'll happen with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:37.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And what'll happen with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we enjoy \Na hot spring bath, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:43.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NGet Away from Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:43.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Get Away from Him
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:46.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:48.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
